t={yMax}\n    numTicksRows={numTicksForHeight(height)}\n    numTicksColumns={numTicksForWidth(width)}\n  />\n);\n```\n\n## Installation\n\n```\nnpm install --save @visx/grid\n```\n","readmeFilename":"Readme.md"}